{
  "stem": "11611.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had to explain to him at great length that by virtue of the paranoia in the United States and the racism that was rampant, the Nisei were out of the question for the Navy.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Army took Nisei in as translators.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I ultimately wound up, as I will tell you, in the Marine Corps.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Marine Corps would borrow Army teams, but they would not use Nisei as translators directly in the Marine Corps.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, [LAUGHS] I was a yeoman second class in civilian clothes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All during the time I was in the Navy, I never put on a-- a sailor suit.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, this was Boulder, Colorado.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were very few ships there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I went in the Marine Corps.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About the early part or middle of 1943.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They asked-- they asked for volunteers, and since I was not a very bright kid at that time, I volunteered for the Marine Corps.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I must-- I must have had some form of death wish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Initially, we were sent out-- there must have been about 40 or 50 of us altogether.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The class consisted of maybe 200, so roughly a quarter of the class went into the Marine Corps.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was volunteers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of the Boulder class, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Boulder ultimately must have turned out about 1,000 people, but I was in almost the first class, and it was roughly 200 people.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think the Marine group was sent to a Camp Elliott near San Diego for a period of two, three months, in which we got our limited military training.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In other words, they showed us what a rifle looked like and a few other important things like that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We learned to march.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By the time I was in the Marine Corps, I had to go buy uniforms.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
